│ alternative debug location (e.g., the first non-PHI instruction in the block).\n\n5. **Conclusion**: This fix ensures that the `DebugLoc` is only used if valid, preventing the assertion failure. The            │
│ alternative debug location provides a reasonable fallback, maintaining the integrity of the debug information."})                                                                                                 │
