│ The issue lies in the code at line 1363, where `BI->setDebugLoc(L->getStartLoc());` is called without verifying if `L->getStartLoc()` is valid. To fix this, we need to add a check to ensure the `DebugLoc` is   │
│ valid before using it. If it is invalid, we should fall back to an alternative debug location, such as the first non-PHI instruction in the block.                                                                │
│                                                                                                                                                                                                                   │
│ Here is the proposed fix:                                                                                                                                                                                         │
│                                                                                                                                                                                                                   │
│ ### Proposed Fix                                                                                                                                                                                                  │
│ Replace:                                                                                                                                                                                                          │
│ ```cpp                                                                                                                                                                                                            │
│ BI->setDebugLoc(L->getStartLoc());                                                                                                                                                                                │
│ ```                                                                                                                                                                                                               │
│                                                                                                                                                                                                                   │
│ With:                                                                                                                                                                                                             │
│ ```cpp                                                                                                                                                                                                            │
│ if (DebugLoc DL = L->getStartLoc())                                                                                                                                                                               │
│   BI->setDebugLoc(DL);                                                                                                                                                                                            │
│ else                                                                                                                                                                                                              │
│   BI->setDebugLoc(BB->getFirstNonPHIOrDbg()->getDebugLoc());                                                                                                                                                      │
│ ```                                                                                                                                                                                                               │
│                                                                                                                                                                                                                   │
│ This ensures that the debug location is only set if valid, and falls back to a reasonable alternative if not.                                                                                                     │
│                                                                                                                                                                                                                   │
│ I will now apply this fix.                                                                                                                                                                                        │
