│ 2. Ensure that the transformation respects the `range` metadata when creating the preheader block and modifying the `icmp` instruction.                                                                           │
│                                                                                                                                                                                                                   │
│ I will now investigate the `SimplifyCFG` transformation to understand how it handles `range` metadata and identify where the fix should be applied.                                                               │
