│ The `SimplifyCFG` transformation handles `MD_range` metadata in the context of masked load/store instructions. Specifically, it ensures that the `range` metadata is preserved when the semantics remain the      │
│ same. This is done by adding the range as a return attribute and copying the metadata to the new instruction.                                                                                                     │
│                                                                                                                                                                                                                   │
│ To fix the issue with the `icmp samesign` transformation, we need to ensure that the `range` metadata is properly propagated when creating the preheader block and modifying the `icmp` instruction. This         │
│ involves:                                                                                                                                                                                                         │
│                                                                                                                                                                                                                   │
│ 1. Checking if the `range` metadata is present on `%x`.                                                                                                                                                           │
│ 2. Propagating the `range` metadata to the new instruction in the preheader block.                                                                                                                                │
│                                                                                                                                                                                                                   │
│ I will now edit the code to implement this fix.                                                                                                                                                                   │
